{
  "text": "Cannabis sativa L. has been reported for the treatment of depression, anxiety, convulsion, Alzheimer, dementia, and insomnia and its constituents responsible for these properties are cannabigerol, tetrahydrocannabinol, and cannabidiol [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] [CITATION_5] .",
